OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,FA delivery driver has told ITV Wales
OL,7,Fabout the stress and pressures of the
OL,8,Fjob as orders for Christmas deliveries
OL,9,Fsoar.
OL,11,FWith his identity protected, Tyler
OL,12,F(not his real name), who has been
OL,13,Fdelivering parcels in mid-Wales for
OL,14,Fover five years, spoke about the
OL,15,Fchallenges he faces while out on
OL,16,Fdeliveries.
