OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,F"On certain days it can be hell on
OL,7,Fearth, absolutely hell on earth," he
OL,8,Fsaid. "You're looking at an extra 50%
OL,9,Fminimum of deliveries; it can be up to
OL,10,F100% on certain rounds. It's
OL,11,Fincredibly difficult to try and keep
OL,12,Fon top of all that."
OL,14,F"There are some drivers I know who
OL,15,Fhave been told by their employers they
OL,16,Fhave 30 seconds for every single drop.
OL,17,FIt's completely impossible."
