OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,FIt comes after new figures from
OL,7,FCitizens Advice found more than a
OL,8,Fthird of people in the UK faced issues
OL,9,Fwith their most recent parcel delivery.
OL,11,FResidents in Powys have called for a
OL,12,Fchange in the way deliveries are made
OL,13,Fin the area after being left
OL,14,Ffrustrated with the service.
OL,16,FClaire Haslam, a local resident,
OL,17,Fprovides a storage box for deliveries
OL,18,Fbut finds they often do not end up
OL,19,Fthere.
