OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,F"It's either at the top of the lane or
OL,7,Fin a field. It's not always in the
OL,8,Fbox," she said.
OL,10,F"I like to shop and I like to support
OL,11,Fthe high street, but where we live,
OL,12,Fit's not always possible. Life's busy."
OL,14,F"This is the talk of the locality at
OL,15,Fthe moment. I was in the pub just last
OL,16,Fnight and the talk was about missed
OL,17,Fdeliveries or deliveries arriving
OL,18,Flate."
