OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,FDiscussing the local parcels depot in
OL,7,FLlandrindod Wells, Claire described it
OL,8,Fas "organised chaos."
OL,10,FShe added: "It's no disrespect to
OL,11,Fthem, but the unit they are operating
OL,12,Ffrom is not fit for purpose. They are
OL,13,Fsorting parcels out in the grassy area
OL,14,Foutside the depot. There were mounds
OL,15,Fof parcels."
