OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,FA spokesperson from Evri, responsible
OL,7,Ffor the depot, said: "We are committed
OL,8,Fto handling every parcel with care and
OL,9,Fthe vast majority of our sites have
OL,10,Frobust cage to car processes in place
OL,11,Fto transfer parcels from the depot to
OL,12,Fthe car.
OL,14,F"In this area, we are actively
OL,15,Freviewing options for a larger
OL,16,Flocation to ensure we maintain the
OL,17,Fhighest standards."
