OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,FDown the road in Knighton, Ben Caine
OL,7,Fhas also experienced issues, with Evri
OL,8,Fdeliveries left in fields behind his
OL,9,Fproperty.
OL,11,FDescribing the search for a missing
OL,12,Fparcel, he said: "It's close, but
OL,13,Ftrying to find it was something a bit
OL,14,Fspecial. I obviously had one from the
OL,15,Fday before, not knowing where it was,
OL,16,Fthen another parcel was left on top of
OL,17,Fit, so they were obviously aware it
OL,18,Fhadn't been collected by me."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
