OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,FBen added that the process of
OL,7,Freporting the issue presented another
OL,8,Fproblem.
OL,10,F"It's a lot of automation, a lot of
OL,11,FAI. Once you get through the AI and
OL,12,Fget to someone, they do talk to you. I
OL,13,Fhave spoken to someone on the phone,
OL,14,Fwhich is very rare. To be honest, they
OL,15,Fjust do it to shut you up and crack
OL,16,Fon; that's the feeling I got."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
