OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,F"I think they need to review the way
OL,7,Fthey treat their staff. They are
OL,8,Fasking them to do too much. Maybe even
OL,9,Flook at the way they pay them, if they
OL,10,Fare paying per drop, that doesn't seem
OL,11,Fto be working. It needs to change, as
OL,12,Fit only seems to be getting worse."
OL,14,FIn response to Ben's experience, Evri
OL,15,Fsaid: "A driver was removed in the
OL,16,Fsummer in relation to this historic
OL,17,Fcase, which doesn't represent the
OL,18,Fcurrent picture of the area, but we
OL,19,Fare committed to resolving any queries
OL,20,Fand delivering for customers in Wales."
