OL,3,C'Hell on earth': Delivery driver on
OL,4,Cdaily toll of deliveries over Christmas
OL,6,FWith increasing demand for deliveries,
OL,7,FTyler says he can often experience
OL,8,Fabuse from customers.
OL,10,FHe's calling for a change in the
OL,11,Fattitude towards delivery drivers.
OL,13,FHe said: "We want to work with the
OL,14,Fcustomers, and we just want the
OL,15,Fcustomers to work with us."
OL,17,F"Things like telling us when where you
OL,18,Fwant your parcels delivered within
OL,19,Freason would be really helpful as well
OL,20,Fas providing post boxes and parcel
OL,21,Fboxes for us to leave parcels in."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
